            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve the <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong></p><p>Once the chicken is golden, return the <strong>leek & garlic mix </strong>to the pan and add the <strong>chicken stock</strong></p><p>Reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1640105213259-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
